name: Starbucks

directions: near the bakery department there are 3 single stall all gender rest rooms, upstairs in the staff area there are 2 more single stall all gender rest rooms that customers can use if the downstairs 3 are occupied.

name: UCSF Alliance Health Project

name: Grace United Church of Christ
directions: through the front door the hallway on your left. The second door.
comment: This church is an Open & Affirming church that is very trans friendly. Any time that there is someone at the church you could stop by if you have to use the bathroom somewhere safe.

name: Five Below

name: The warren youth project
directions: The toilets are oppersite the main door and around the staircases throughout the building
comment: You can go into any of the toilets in the building no matter what gender you are as long as you are aged between 16-25

Goldfish Swim School

name: Riley
